                            <li>Improved customer service for clients like Tesco and Lidl.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Reference 3 - Industrial Door Services (IDS) -->
                <div class="bg-secondary-bg rounded-xl card-shadow border-b-4 border-accent/80 overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/652e90c1583f67a8de233f2d/67d97e1f6abcbe2751689426_IDS.webp" 
                         alt="Industrial facility with large automatic doors and signage." 
                         class="w-full h-40 object-cover" 
                         onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/600x200/00A3FF/ffffff?text=IDS+Image+Unavailable'">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <h4 class="font-extrabold text-2xl text-accent mb-3">Industrial Door Services (IDS)</h4>
